data.description:
Agent Simulation is an action, simulation, and strategy game in which each player shows their targeting skills and agility against enemies in a virtual environment. At the end of each mission, you will collect medals and earn various certificates with these medals. At the end of the game, these certificates will prove your strength as an agent and help you to receive your agent license. 
In each level of the Agent Simulation, you will be evaluated according to your targeting skills. Before the limited time provided ends, you must kill all your enemies. Every successful head shot will get you more points! Sometimes you will be asked to complete the missions in such a limited time, you have to be fast and agile!
There will be three options offered in each level and those options will constantly change! For example, double bullets, double damage, slowing time down, blocking bullets or extra life, etc. You can strategize using any of these options!  
Fight to be the best!

data.description:
In the lush and enchanting world of Monkey Swingers, players embark on a thrilling journey through a magical forest filled with captivating wonders. As they swing through the treetops, players take control of adorable monkeys, each with its unique personality and style. The forest comes alive with lush foliage, and playful critters, creating a visually stunning and immersive gaming experience.

Amidst this captivating forest lies the heart of the game - a whimsical cosmetics shop. Here, players can use the bananas they collect during their adventures to unlock an array of delightful cosmetic items. From funky hats to fashionable outfits and amusing accessories, the customization options are endless, allowing players to create their signature look and stand out as they swing from vine to vine.

Monkey Swingers also offers a delightful twist with a low-gravity area tucked away in the forest. This mystical region defies the laws of physics, granting monkeys the ability to defy gravity and perform gravity-defying stunts. Players can climb on the walls of massive trees, scale towering cliffs, and navigate through perplexing mazes with ease, all while experiencing a thrilling sense of freedom and excitement. The low-gravity area introduces an element of surprise and challenge, keeping players engaged as they master the art of acrobatics.

The game features a diverse range of levels that progressively increase in difficulty. From simple to mind-bendingly tricky!

data.description:
**FEAR VR: Unleash Nightmares in the Virtual Jungle**

Embark on a spine-chilling adventure with "FEAR VR," a gorilla tag fangame redefining horror in virtual reality. Traverse a haunted virtual jungle, surrounded by nightmarish gorillas corrupted by an unknown force. Dilapidated structures and twisted vegetation set the stage for heart-pounding encounters, challenging you to survive relentless pursuit.

**The Setting: A Virtual Nightmare Unveiled**

"FEAR VR" plunges you into a desolate virtual jungle, blending haunting beauty with oppressive darkness. Explore abandoned research facilities and eerie landscapes as you uncover the mysteries of this gorilla-infested nightmare.

**The Gorillas: More Than Meets the Eye**

Twisted and malevolent, the gorillas were once guardians turned hunters. Their primal instincts drive them to relentlessly pursue, with every growl a reminder that danger lurks. Encountering them is a confrontation with your deepest fears.

**Gameplay: Heart-Pounding Escape**

Survival is paramount in "FEAR VR." Navigate intricate corridors and landscapes, outsmarting pursuing gorillas. Each decision becomes a matter of life or death, adding intensity to every heart-pounding escape.

**Immersive Audio: The Sound of Fear**

The game's audio experience heightens the sense of dread, from distant echoes to subtle whispers. The chilling soundtrack draws players deeper into the virtual nightmare.

- Improve display of damage numbers
- Improved typing sound in tutorials

- Add more buildings to planets

data.description:
Game flow
 Select from 3 difficulty levels and start the game
Keep killing zombies until the game is over
 When it's over, shoot yourself in the head to end the game (return to home screen)


Scoreboard item explanation
TIME: Survival time (does not affect score)
KILL: Number of zombies killed (zombies killed with a knife are not counted)
HIT RATE: Hit rate (number of shots  number of zombies defeated x 100)
SCORE: Total number of KILL  HIT RATE


Strategy points
In DARKNESS mode, listen to the footsteps of zombies and search for enemies while shining a light on them (be careful as gunshots make it difficult to hear footsteps!)
In a pinch, use a knife and stay calm!
When aiming for a high score, avoid using full auto as much as possible and try to hit with one shot!

data.description:
Sideways Runners is a competitive multiplayer VR game that innovatively uses hand-driven locomotion. This game sets itself apart by not featuring a traditional racing mode, instead focusing on a variety of game modes that range from casual play to more structured formats like paintball, along with the exciting addition of user-created minigames.

Players can engage in different game modes that cater to varying levels of competitiveness and skill. While the game allows for the creation of custom minigames, these cannot be shared globally; instead, players must invite others to join them directly for private sessions. This feature adds a personal touch to the gameplay, as players can craft unique experiences and then compete or collaborate directly with friends or other enthusiasts they invite.

The competitive spirit of Sideways Runners is further enhanced by its daily reward system, where players earn 100 in-game currency each day they log on. This currency can be spent on a variety of cosmetic items, allowing players to personalize their avatars with different skins, accessories, and animations, enhancing their identity in the game's vibrant virtual world.

Sideways Runners stands out by offering a physically engaging, strategy-oriented VR experience with a diverse range of gameplay options, fostering both community involvement and competitive fervor.
